- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with improving the performance of word representations, which is a key task in AI. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a possible category as the paper discusses benchmark tasks that are commonly used in information retrieval. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a possible category as the paper deals with neural network-based word representations.
